                            <span>VERIFIED DEVELOPER CREDENTIALS:</span>
                        </div>
                        <strong class="text-white text-base block font-bold tracking-wide mb-1 uppercase font-mono-tech">MOHAMAD HARTADI (ADI)</strong>
