                            <p>🔵 <b>FB:</b> <a href="https://web.facebook.com/m.hartadi/" target="_blank" class="text-cyan-400 underline font-bold">facebook.com/m.hartadi/</a></p>
                            <p>📱 <b>WhatsApp:</b> <a href="https://wa.me/6282231036047" target="_blank" class="text-emerald-400 font-bold underline">082231036047</a></p>
